-----------------------------
Installation:

Just place or extract the cstrike folder into your Counter-Strike: Source directory. For example place the files in these directories: "C:\Program Files/Steam/steamapps/"your user name"/counter strike source/cstrike/maps/.../models/...materials/" The "...'s" being each sub folder inside the the main folder tiled "cstrike."

-----------------------------
NOTES:

This is a remake of fy_mm4a1 from CS 1.6 to Counter-Strike: SOURCE. Its not a perfect remake I just did the best I could from memory. 

-------------------------------

Description:

Its a very plain map so just cause its a source remake dosen't mean I made it all super awesome or nothing. But it looks nicer then before(graphix wise) 

 +Works with bots 

 +Has like 32, 16vs16, spawn points

 +Comes with a few different weapons

 +Granades and AWP's are on the top bridge over looking the fighting area
 
 +Boxs and bushes are now in the map

-------------------------------
